bwapi

Class TilePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • bwapi.AbstractPoint<TilePosition>
      • bwapi.TilePosition

  • public class TilePosition
extends AbstractPoint<TilePosition>
    Build Tiles - each build tile is a 4x4 square of walk tiles, or a 32x32 square of pixels. These are called build tiles because buildability data is available at this resolution, and correspond to the tiles seen in game. For example, a Command Center occupies an area of 4x3 build tiles.
